    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市将因利率担忧重燃而下滑：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们再次担心美联储将在更长时间内维持高利率，助长了美国基准股指的抛售，并推高了债券收益率和美元，亚洲股市将于 5 月开盘走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维京邮轮 IPO 融资 15.4 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cruise-line-viking-holdings-ipo-is-said-to-fetch-1-54-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，维京控股有限公司 (Viking Holdings Ltd.) 的首次公开募股定价接近市场定价区间的上限，为这家豪华游轮运营商和两名投资者筹集 15.4 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cruise-line-viking-holdings-ipo-is-said-to-fetch-1-54-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:28:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元的剧烈波动只是未来的一个尝试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-30/jpy-usd-japanese-yen-s-slide-and-dramatic-rebound-are-just-the-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[除非深层次的结构性问题得到解决，否则剧烈波动可能会更加频繁。其影响远远超出了日本。]]></description>
